	<Title>
		Zinc for colds: The final word?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Everyone&apos;s heard of taking zinc for colds. No one knew it worked &amp;mdash; until now.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Will taking zinc for colds make my colds go away faster?
	</Question>
